    </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Influenza H2N2</td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Oseltamivir
     <xref ref-type="table-fn" rid="tfn21-rmmj-11-3-e0027">§</xref>
    </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">AIDS</td>
    <td valign="top" align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">&gt;20 antiviral drugs grouped in 8 classes and &gt;40 combinations of two or more drugs</td>
